(42, 2, 23, 2, 22, 29, 29, 'Every male that openeth the womb', 'Connection of Firstborn Dedication', 'Both passages emphasize the importance of dedicating the firstborn to the Lord. Luke 2:23 references the law that every male opening the womb is holy, paralleling Exodus 22:29''s command to give the firstborn of sons to God.', 'theme', 0.391, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(42, 2, 23, 4, 3, 13, 13, 'Every male that openeth the womb', 'Connection of Firstborn Sanctity', 'This connection highlights the sanctity of the firstborn. Both passages emphasize that the firstborn are set apart and holy to the Lord.', 'theme', 0.391, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
